	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=114513><span id=Scholar>Larney</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>303 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>At level 30 many of the lower level MOBs won't aggro on you until you sit down. If you invis yourself, there are still plenty of undead around that can bug you while you meditate. At level 30 you might mess with the mobs called &quot;a skeleton&quot; which drop pretty good loot, but hit hard for their level. These are usually solo-able at 29 and up, since they are spaced well away from higher MOBs in most cases and the lower ones shouldn't aggro on you unless your health gets real low. I wouldn't go soloing Najena at 30 though, as her company keeps her pretty well guarded.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Apr 16 05:56:36 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=205888 target=_new><b>Larney Silversmith</b></a><br><i>Paladin of Firiona Vie</i></td></td></tr>
